[SQLAlchemy Migrations Using Flask-Migrate]

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNmWxvvyBGU

[Update Requirements.txt]
pip freeze > requirements.txt


[Model Change]
flask db init
flask db upgrade
flask db migrate
Install Flask-Migrate using pip:  pip install Flask-Migrate

Create a migration repository by running the following command in your terminal:
- flask db init
Create an initial migration by running the following command:
- flask db migrate -m "initial migration"
Apply the migration to the database by running the following command:
- flask db upgrade


[venv activate]
python -m venv venv
